      "author": "kja140",
      "description": "Incremental reading and spaced repetition for Obsidian. First public release prepared for community-plugin submission.\n\n- SuperMemo-style single queue: topics (A-Factor) interleaved with cards (FSRS-6)\n- Extracts from selection, clipboard, and PDFs\n- Flashcards: clipboard, image, and image occlusion\n- Inline cards parsed from note bodies (Q::A, {{c1::}}, ==highlight== cloze)\n- Knowledge tree view and Dataview dashboard\n- Sioyek PDF integration (desktop only)",
